data.description: Beautiful ranch home on an oversized lot, with room to build lots of new equity! The large deck overlooks the coy pond and lazy river in the backyard. The upper level boast two bedrooms, a full bath, large kitchen, dining room and living room. Finished, walk-out basement provides cozy living room with wood burning stove, a 3/4 bath, and an oversized master with sitting area. home in the Cimarron Hills neighborhood, you don't want to miss this amazing opportunity!
